    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Fog Cloud</strong> (Level 1 Conjuration)</p><p>You create a 20-foot-radius sphere of fog centered on a point within range. The sphere spreads around corners, and its area is heavily obscured. It lasts for the duration or until a wind of moderate or greater speed (at least 10 miles per hour) disperses it.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the radius of the fog increases by 20 feet for each slot level above 1st.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 120 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 1 hour (Concentration)</p><p><em>Classes: Druid, Ranger, Sorcerer, Wizard</em></p>",
